pageTitle: River/Parkland at River Ridge Golf Club in Sealy
TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {5674=The 18-hole River/Parkland at River Ridge Golf Club in Sealy, TX is a public golf course that opened in 1998. Designed by Jay Riviere, River/Parkland at River Ridge Golf Club measures 6946 yards from the longest tees and has a slope rating of 129 and a 73.3 USGA rating. The course features 4 sets of tees for different skill levels. The greens are bermuda grass.}
